# One deployment serves multiple users securely!

# =============================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# =============================================================================

# - NEVER commit real credentials to git/GitHub
# - Set real values ONLY in your hosting platform's environment variables
# - Use a strong, random UEX_WEBHOOK_SECRET if you enable webhook validation
# - Keep your bot token secure - treat it like a password
# - The bot will only send DMs to the configured DISCORD_USER_ID 